#Included Patches

alwayscenter - Makes floating windows default to center

bottomstack(no bstackhoriz) - Master and stack but the stack is on the bottom

centeredmaster(no centeredfloatingmaster) - Master in center surrounded on either side by stacks

cool-autostart - Autostart anything with dwm and kill when dwm is killed

fancybar - Show all windows in status bar

gaplessgrid - All windows are placed in a grid, basically no master

removeborder - Removes border when there is only one window

pertag - Keeps layout and other settings per tag

restartsig - Restart dwm with a HUP signal or by key combo

rotate stack - Rotates all windows clockwise or counter clockwise

stackmfack - Change size of stack window in stack

sticky - Make window appear on all tags

warp - Move mouse to center of new focused window

